[I] A framework for smart card readers

[T] OpenCT is a library for accessing smart card terminals. It provides
[T] a rich set of functions for driver writers, protocol drivers for T=0
[T] and T=1, serial and USB functionality, including USB hotplugging. The
[T] main user of OpenCT is the OpenSC smart card framework, but OpenCT
[T] can of course be used by other applications as well. OpenCT provides
[T] a native OpenCT, CT-API and PC/SC Lite IFD interface with an OpenCT
[T] ifdhandler resource manager.

[U] http://www.opensc-project.org/

